62
00:05:28,270 --> 00:05:30,400
It was you who taught me how to be human.

63
00:05:30,870 --> 00:05:32,870
Fei Zheng, Fei Zheng.

64
00:05:41,120 --> 00:05:43,360
Fei Zheng, Fei Zheng.

65
00:05:45,430 --> 00:05:47,270
You really can act.

66
00:05:48,270 --> 00:05:50,070
Every word comes
from the bottom of my heart.

67
00:05:50,070 --> 00:05:51,800
Can you guarantee that for so many years,

68
00:05:51,800 --> 00:05:53,600
