81
00:06:39,800 --> 00:06:40,680
Fine.

82
00:06:43,240 --> 00:06:44,680
Then I

83
00:06:45,680 --> 00:06:47,270
thank you, Your Majesty.

84
00:06:54,070 --> 00:06:55,720
You wish to die?

85
00:06:59,240 --> 00:07:00,070
Fei Zheng,

86
00:07:00,630 --> 00:07:02,830
