with your own eyes.

90
00:07:09,240 --> 00:07:10,560
Watch closely.

91
00:07:24,190 --> 00:07:25,190
Your Majesty!

92
00:07:25,750 --> 00:07:28,210
When the Changmo army
breaches the capital,

93
00:07:28,830 --> 00:07:31,160
