94
00:07:39,159 --> 00:07:40,090
What did you say?

95
00:07:42,070 --> 00:07:43,070
I said

96
00:07:44,070 --> 00:07:46,530
when the Changmo army
breaches the capital,

97
00:07:46,750 --> 00:07:48,800
it will be too late for you to kill...

