110
00:08:34,390 --> 00:08:35,909
When you have time,

111
00:08:36,840 --> 00:08:39,630
I hope you can go back and visit there.

112
00:08:40,440 --> 00:08:42,000
I wish you

113
00:08:42,440 --> 00:08:44,440
