114
00:08:45,120 --> 00:08:48,480
May Jinglan be peaceful forever.

115
00:08:49,870 --> 00:08:50,960
Chu.

116
00:09:22,630 --> 00:09:23,720
I just

117
00:09:24,150 --> 00:09:26,030
personally killed Fei Zheng.

118
00:09:34,600 --> 00:09:36,260
You forced Liu Xie to her death

119
00:09:37,030 --> 00:09:38,240
and killed Fei Zheng.

120
00:09:39,000 --> 00:09:40,660
Who are you going to kill next?

121
00:09:42,080 --> 00:09:43,840
Who else do you have left?

122
00:09:44,480 --> 00:09:45,960
Xiao Chi fights for you,

123
00:09:46,480 --> 00:09:48,540
and Han Yunling treats your illness.

124
00:09:49,670 --> 00:09:51,080
They are useful to you.

125
00:09:51,630 --> 00:09:52,840
The next one

126
00:09:53,670 --> 00:09:54,840
will be me, right?

127
00:09:56,480 --> 00:09:58,010
What are you talking about?

128
00:09:58,600 --> 00:09:59,910
Your father has already brought his troops

129
00:09:59,910 --> 00:10:01,630
