177
00:14:49,150 --> 00:14:50,750
I will definitely come back.

178
00:14:50,910 --> 00:14:51,480
Yeah.

179
00:15:50,240 --> 00:15:51,480
Xiao Chi!

180
00:15:51,480 --> 00:15:52,750
Your life belongs to me!

181
00:15:52,750 --> 00:15:54,270
You must come back alive!

182
00:15:56,720 --> 00:15:57,510
