183
00:16:18,080 --> 00:16:19,270
Changmo is invading.

184
00:16:19,270 --> 00:16:20,800
We have nowhere to retreat.

185
00:16:20,960 --> 00:16:23,240
Behind us are our parents

186
00:16:23,240 --> 00:16:24,100
and loved ones.

187
00:16:24,630 --> 00:16:25,870
We absolutely can't retreat!

188
00:16:25,870 --> 00:16:28,270
-We absolutely can't retreat!
-We absolutely can't retreat!

189
00:16:28,270 --> 00:16:31,730
-We absolutely can't retreat!
-We absolutely can't retreat!

190
00:16:33,840 --> 00:16:35,030
Consort Ling,

191
00:16:35,150 --> 00:16:36,320
