195
00:16:59,670 --> 00:17:00,670
Don't overthink it.

196
00:17:00,670 --> 00:17:02,440
I was just afraid you'd lose my treasure

197
00:17:02,440 --> 00:17:04,040
and couldn't return it to me.

198
00:17:04,240 --> 00:17:05,569
Please be very careful.

199
00:17:05,920 --> 00:17:07,030
Destroy Jinglan,

200
00:17:07,550 --> 00:17:09,810
