201
00:17:10,270 --> 00:17:11,310
Soldiers!

202
00:17:11,720 --> 00:17:12,960
Father!

203
00:17:16,550 --> 00:17:17,750
Father!

204
00:17:20,200 --> 00:17:21,310
Father!

205
00:17:25,069 --> 00:17:26,510
Father!

206
00:17:36,640 --> 00:17:38,200
Father!

207
00:17:54,110 --> 00:17:54,960
Father!

208
00:17:55,830 --> 00:17:57,490
Withdraw the troops, Father!

209
00:17:57,750 --> 00:17:58,960
Let's go home.

210
00:18:00,830 --> 00:18:02,920
I miss home.

211
00:18:15,110 --> 00:18:16,960
You promised me.

212
00:18:17,110 --> 00:18:18,720
Jinglan and Changmo

213
00:18:19,160 --> 00:18:20,720
