215
00:18:22,030 --> 00:18:23,440
You said so!

216
00:18:25,440 --> 00:18:27,100
Withdraw the troops, Father.

217
00:18:29,720 --> 00:18:30,880
Father.

218
00:18:31,960 --> 00:18:33,480
Jinglan and Changmo

219
00:18:34,830 --> 00:18:36,510
