220
00:18:37,270 --> 00:18:39,510
We can't fight anymore.

221
00:18:41,880 --> 00:18:43,750
Father, I beg you.

222
00:18:44,240 --> 00:18:45,400
Father.

223
00:18:57,750 --> 00:18:58,920
All troops, charge!

224
00:18:58,920 --> 00:19:02,830
-Charge!
-Charge!

225
00:19:05,310 --> 00:19:06,480
-Charge!
-Charge!

226
00:19:12,750 --> 00:19:16,400
