229
00:20:14,350 --> 00:20:16,200
My child...

230
00:20:28,440 --> 00:20:29,750
Wanyu!

231
00:20:30,680 --> 00:20:31,640
My child.

232
00:20:32,270 --> 00:20:33,240
Don't be afraid.

233
00:20:33,240 --> 00:20:33,920
I am here.

234
00:20:34,680 --> 00:20:35,590
I can't...

235
00:20:35,720 --> 00:20:37,030
It's too late.

236
00:20:51,680 --> 00:20:53,010
Protect the bloodline!

237
00:20:59,480 --> 00:21:00,590
