You've knocked away all my wishes
when you fell.

242
00:22:21,160 --> 00:22:22,310
Then I wish you

243
00:22:22,310 --> 00:22:23,970
could find your beloved soon.

244
00:22:25,000 --> 00:22:27,310
Actually, I think I've found her.

245
00:22:30,720 --> 00:22:31,480
What am I

246
00:22:31,920 --> 00:22:33,920
