247
00:22:35,550 --> 00:22:36,790
My husband.

248
00:22:40,270 --> 00:22:43,110
I wish to trade my life for yours.

249
00:22:44,240 --> 00:22:45,720
I'm fine now.

250
00:22:46,920 --> 00:22:48,850
