251
00:22:49,510 --> 00:22:50,960
I used to love you so much.

252
00:22:51,510 --> 00:22:53,750
I was willing to give you everything.

253
00:22:54,270 --> 00:22:55,880
You only love yourself.

254
00:23:10,240 --> 00:23:11,640
Get the child back for me!

255
