263
00:23:51,480 --> 00:23:52,200
Wanyu.

264
00:23:52,200 --> 00:23:53,600
Yunling, hurry up and go.

265
00:23:53,960 --> 00:23:54,920
General Xiao.

266
00:23:55,350 --> 00:23:57,750
General Xiao, I'm counting on you.

267
00:23:57,750 --> 00:23:58,830
Hurry, go.

268
00:23:58,830 --> 00:23:59,890
What should you do?

269
00:24:00,310 --> 00:24:01,570
Don't bother about me.

270
00:24:53,000 --> 00:24:56,030
Xiao Chi!

271
00:24:56,030 --> 00:24:57,750
Kill!

272
00:26:29,750 --> 00:26:30,750
Your Majesty!

273
00:26:32,310 --> 00:26:33,880
I have held the city gates!

274
00:26:37,350 --> 00:26:38,830
Please, Your Majesty,

275
00:26:39,240 --> 00:26:40,830
