276
00:27:34,750 --> 00:27:35,750
You will

277
00:27:37,680 --> 00:27:39,440
never see my child again.

278
00:27:42,920 --> 00:27:43,920
I wish you

279
00:27:44,720 --> 00:27:45,550
a long

280
00:27:46,830 --> 00:27:48,070
and healthy life.

281
00:29:05,680 --> 00:29:06,680
Your Majesty,

282
00:29:07,270 --> 00:29:09,800
