on the battlefield.

283
00:29:10,160 --> 00:29:11,440
It was so chaotic.

284
00:29:11,720 --> 00:29:12,960
Even if the baby had been born,

285
00:29:12,960 --> 00:29:14,070
it probably

286
00:29:14,350 --> 00:29:15,750
couldn't have survived.

287
00:29:16,270 --> 00:29:17,310
Where is

288
00:29:19,110 --> 00:29:20,680
Han Yunling?

289
00:29:22,440 --> 00:29:23,750
Wasn't she

290
00:29:25,510 --> 00:29:27,830
