inside and outside the city,

292
00:29:30,750 --> 00:29:32,280
but there's no trace of her.

293
00:29:35,240 --> 00:29:36,590
Bury

294
00:29:37,510 --> 00:29:39,570
all the surrendered soldiers alive.

295
00:29:39,750 --> 00:29:40,240
But...

296
00:29:40,550 --> 00:29:42,810
that's hundreds of thousands of people.

297
00:29:43,440 --> 00:29:44,480
Kill them.

298
00:29:46,070 --> 00:29:47,110
Yes.

299
00:30:52,830 --> 00:30:53,790
Aunt,

300
00:30:53,880 --> 00:30:56,590
why do we come here

301
00:30:56,590 --> 00:30:58,240
on this day every year?

302
00:31:01,030 --> 00:31:02,680
Because from here, we can see

303
00:31:02,680 --> 00:31:03,960
Jinglan in the east.

304
00:31:04,350 --> 00:31:06,070
Why do we see Jinglan?

305
00:31:08,030 --> 00:31:08,960
Because...

306
00:31:11,510 --> 00:31:13,310
the people who love us are there.

307
00:31:17,400 --> 00:31:18,350
Aunt,

308
00:31:18,350 --> 00:31:20,110
I want candied hawthorn.

309
00:31:20,830 --> 00:31:22,960
The candied hawthorn stall isn't open yet.

310
00:31:22,960 --> 00:31:25,220
After I finish treating the new general,

311
00:31:25,440 --> 00:31:26,350
I'll buy you candied hawthorn,

312
00:31:26,350 --> 00:31:26,960
okay?

313
00:31:27,200 --> 00:31:27,680
Be good.

314
00:31:27,680 --> 00:31:28,240
Okay.

315
00:31:56,110 --> 00:31:57,110
Yue.

316
00:31:57,350 --> 00:31:58,350
Don't touch that.

317
00:31:58,480 --> 00:32:00,350
It belongs to someone else.

318
00:32:27,200 --> 00:32:28,920
I'm back.
